Sanitation facilities
This is in addition to a plethora of sanitation facilities like extra water supply and storage facilities, expanded common facilities like dining halls and accompanying infrastructure. The school re-entry emergency to-do list includes replacement — on temporary or permanent basis — of thousands of elderly teachers and those with underlying health conditions, who have since been exempted from teaching duties over extra risks they face under the Covid menace. It is a fact that even during normal times, shortage of teachers was still a problem.



