Among ideas worth considering is how county governments, elected leaders (CDF management and legislative enablement on issues like by-passing normal procurement procedures), schools could create and combine synergies with other institutions like technical training institutions (Tvets and polytechnics), the military, the National Youth Service (NYS) to quickly deliver the physical facilities needed and at minimal cost.



